# DevFlow own state (dogfooding)
.devflow/state.json
.devflow/lock
.devflow/last-ship.json

# DevFlow phase plans — the `.planning/` directory is DevFlow's tracked
# phase-plan convention. `phase_prompt()` reads .planning/ROADMAP.md and
# .planning/phases/NN-*/CONTEXT.md, so those files are kept committable.
# Only top-level scratch files under .planning/ are ignored.
# See ARCHITECTURE.md and CONTRIBUTING.md.
.planning/*
!.planning/ROADMAP.md
!.planning/PROJECT.md
!.planning/phases/

# Git worktrees created by `devflow start --worktree` / `parallel` / `sequentagent`
.worktrees/
